OL,3,CLady Gaga and Jay Z fashion designer
OL,4,Cof the starts crafts new mayoral robe
OL,6,FA fashion designer who can count
OL,7,Finternational superstars among his
OL,8,Fclients has restored the mayor of
OL,9,FCarlisle's robe and created a new one
OL,10,Fto last 50 years.
OL,12,FLee Paton from Cumbria has previously
OL,13,Fcreated pieces for Lady Gaga and Jay Z.
OL,15,FHe offered to restore the 45-year-old
OL,16,Fmayoral robe and create a replica when
OL,17,Fthe Charter Trustees of the City of
OL,18,FCarlisle decided to spend over #12,000
OL,19,Fon commissioning a replacement
OL,20,Fceremonial garb.
