OL,3,CLady Gaga and Jay Z fashion designer
OL,4,Cof the starts crafts new mayoral robe
OL,6,FMr Paton offered his services for
OL,7,F#3,500 less, and promised to involve
OL,8,Flocal students in the making process.
OL,10,FHe told ITV Border: "Heritage skills
OL,11,Fin general are at risk, so one of the
OL,12,Fthings I wanted to do when I returned
OL,13,Fto Cumbria was to encourage local
OL,14,Fpeople to learn some of those craft
OL,15,Fskills."
OL,17,FThe fashion designer moved back to
OL,18,FCumbria in 2021, having lived in
OL,19,FLondon for two decades. The robe is
OL,20,Fthe first project of his Newbiggin-
OL,21,Fbased business, Godener.
