OL,3,CLady Gaga and Jay Z fashion designer
OL,4,Cof the starts crafts new mayoral robe
OL,6,FCreating the robe includes fine
OL,7,Fneedlework, from delicate embroidery
OL,8,Fto using gold threads.
OL,10,FMr Paton said: "There are 69 mini
OL,11,Frosettes on the new robe, and I'm
OL,12,Fexpecting them to take 45 minutes
OL,13,F(each).
OL,15,F"All of the hand embroidery and fine
OL,16,Fdetails that are going into it are
OL,17,Fwhat I love to do, it's been a really
OL,18,Fpleasurable project to get to grips
OL,19,Fwith."
