OL,3,CLady Gaga and Jay Z fashion designer
OL,4,Cof the starts crafts new mayoral robe
OL,6,FOne of the students involved in the
OL,7,Frestoration, Julie Huddart, said: "The
OL,8,Fprice for each sequin, and how much
OL,9,Fgold is in the thread... it makes you
OL,10,Fa bit nervous that you're handling
OL,11,Fthings that are so expensive.
OL,13,F"It's been really exciting to be
OL,14,Finvolved, see the old robes and see
OL,15,Fhow the restoration takes place."
OL,17,FThe first mayor to wear the robe is
OL,18,FCarlisle's current mayor, Councillor
OL,19,FJeanette Whalen.
