OL,3,CLady Gaga and Jay Z fashion designer
OL,4,Cof the starts crafts new mayoral robe
OL,6,FCllr Whalen said: "The old one was
OL,7,Fheavy, and there was no padding to put
OL,8,Fpins in to hold the chain in place...
OL,9,Fit was wearing heavily.
OL,11,F"The (new) robe is light and not so
OL,12,Fdifficult to wear, it's much better
OL,13,Ffor mayors going into ceremonies. It
OL,14,Factually feels comfortable, whereas
OL,15,Fthe other one was uncomfortable and
OL,16,Fbulky.
OL,18,F"I'm not quite Lady Gaga or Jay Z, but
OL,19,FI think the people of Carlisle deserve
OL,20,Fto have the best, so I feel very
OL,21,Fprivileged to be in this position."
