OL,3,CLady Gaga and Jay Z fashion designer
OL,4,Cof the starts crafts new mayoral robe
OL,6,FCllr Whalen says the poor condition of
OL,7,Fthe old mayoral robe was obvious: "At
OL,8,Fthe beginning of my mayoral year you
OL,9,Fcould see the old robe had seen wear
OL,10,Fand tear through many years. It was
OL,11,Fbecoming unwearable, but also
OL,12,Funfixable.
OL,14,F"We were going to events and had to
OL,15,Fcheck every time that it was OK to
OL,16,Fwear. That's not a situation you want
OL,17,Fto be in."
OL,19,FCllr Whalen emphasised the importance
OL,20,Fof Carlisle College students getting
OL,21,Finvolved in the making of the robe.
