OL,3,CLady Gaga and Jay Z fashion designer
OL,4,Cof the starts crafts new mayoral robe
OL,6,FCarlisle's mayor said: "It's an
OL,7,Fextraordinary opportunity for some of
OL,8,Fthe students to participate, and be
OL,9,Fpart of that unique history, alongside
OL,10,Fthe fact that this gown is expected to
OL,11,Flast for 50 years.
OL,13,F"It's key that young people get an
OL,14,Fopportunity like this, because it
OL,15,Fdoesn't often come around. Any
OL,16,Fopportunities like that should be
OL,17,Fgrabbed with both hands... it's real
OL,18,Fhistory, it's not just reading it from
OL,19,Fa textbook."
